{"id": "854ff9a6c2a9c9ea68c836b79631cd50b1d2b197ef19b0bb9b7ee53b517aef8f", "item_id": "3fa5491387:0", "text": "RenderMan for Houdini needs to be installed for the full functionality of RenderMan in Solaris."}
{"id": "2ef550844c7ce85eeb6258c8bca2651538547746feb51931e10ed9786cc9baa4", "item_id": "3fa5491387:1", "text": "RenderMan supports the native USD \"Solaris\" workflows introduced in Houdini 18.  Solaris offers artists and TDs:"}
{"id": "d035a632dcf9ded2aaef05604cd678341703e48d9ca54ea02d5680781b4c25df", "item_id": "3fa5491387:2", "text": "Access to native USD for scene composition, variants, and overrides.  USD is a robust technology for building up assets, putting them into sets, and adding shot-specific details and animation.  It is a great pipeline tool."}
{"id": "a6e8b381f03c215b34ac358028f72e59b2ee51dd387a2f90a1b66e2c110c9d63", "item_id": "3fa5491387:3", "text": "A new lighting toolset that allows artists to build lights into their USD scenes."}
{"id": "d72187721b783b9c751f9389024a45ef7b33dac61e6ff5771faca1527ed797dd", "item_id": "3fa5491387:4", "text": "Direct batch rendering of USD files via Houdini's \"husk\" command-line renderer."}
{"id": "626cbcc98a9e8fe386843ea9957a4502bcd298fb601e525d26507ec261431219", "item_id": "3fa5491387:5", "text": "RenderMan provides a USD Hydra Renderer Delegate that allows artists to render interactively directly to the Solaris viewport."}
{"id": "183ead71f39e12a3cfa5f6bf89b2e39899589e8232e2e19a7f4517837fadfe6a", "item_id": "3fa5491387:6", "text": "Artists get immediate path-traced visual feedback during scene assembly, and adjustments to lighting, materials, and other scene attributes.  The same RenderMan Hydra Renderer Delegate is what also allows the \"husk\" command-line renderer."}
{"id": "e1275c04fe2ac561d966d8ab0e3962432dfe09e7082ae3c00b15a3f835ab8f71", "item_id": "3fa5491387:7", "text": "As the SideFX builds on Solaris, RenderMan will continue to provide deep matching integrations to new features and capabilities."}
{"id": "4aa99c6602fcf1f78ec126ed8065bbda8047f12d000cec849b10e978e1283204", "item_id": "3fa5491387:8", "text": "For more information, please consult the other sections of our documentation, as well as the USD documentation and the Solaris documentation:"}
{"id": "d7cdb7068b1e0c4ff191d4706f9f473defa065626e8f65b7322569c1d4da5e3b", "item_id": "3fa5491387:9", "text": "RenderMan for Houdini – Solaris:"}
